The Atlantis-simulated survey diet composition for the mskeyrun project

Source: R/simSurveyDietcomp.r
simSurveyDietcomp.Rd

Simulated survey diet composition data from Atlantis model as sampled by atlantisom

simSurveyDietcomp

Format

A data frame

ModSim

Atlantis model name and simulation id

year

year simulated survey conducted

Code

Atlantis model three letter code for predator group

Name

Atlantis model common name for predator group

survey

simulated survey name

agecl

age class of Atlantis functional group

prey

Atlantis model common name for prey group

variable

proportion in diet (dietprop)

value

value of the variable

units

units of the variable
